node.text:
GIVEAWAY 🏙🎉 Who wants $500 to explore the vibrant @hudsonsquareproperties neighborhood? 

Enter To Win: Tag a friend you'd explore with & Follow @hudsonsquareproperties
(Winner will receive a $500 visa gift card to use for a day of exploring Hudson Square)

From a handful of art installations, urban spaces like Restorative Ground, restaurants, & of course the iconic Hudson River Park...There's no shortage of things to do this summer. See our stories + Link-In-Bio for the full guide @newyork_instagram  #Partner #HudsonSquare #NYC 
-- Giveaway not affiliated with IG, value $500, will end on 11:59 EST 8/12. Selection details & terms: bit.ly/bucketlistterms
